Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一節課是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣又熱  又碰上紫外線這個女生的天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:38.03,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  開始打掃泳池啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修一  看我的地板刷如何高效地工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一兩下就刷得它閃閃發亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南  你不掃除嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃除只能加快泳池開放的進度  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來千秋你不會游泳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  就算千秋一個人偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點大小的泳池光我一個就能搞定…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌控水源亦既掌控泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌控水源亦既掌控掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我握著水管就別想掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來搶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶？怎麼搶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去只能眼睜睜看著泳池乾掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:01:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不喜歡別人對我不理不睬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我最討厭的是動不動就放棄的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是希望我們理她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎麼辦呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位過來下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:18.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（作戰會議）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿水桶裝些水來  不然掃除不能進行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前因後果我們都瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把水管交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去鄰鎮的游泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會幫你練習的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能太嚴格哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對症下藥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意力從水管上移開這一刻我等了好久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎是嗎  戰略就是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱…抱歉  南
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟悉水性實踐才是王道  是這個道理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服濕了 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淋浴囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心個什麼勁兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下大家都成落湯雞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…那個…衣…衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  真  把水桶拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早料到會如此已經拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  你還真會做人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣站好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田用掃帚  吉野用水管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別熱啊熱啊地叫個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都覺得熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是真的很熱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在越熱上體育課就越舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  今天有游泳課
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱到極限時  跳進游泳池的瞬間也是舒服到極點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱啊熱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊  人可是陸生動物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸生動物幹嘛要會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會游泳也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  會游泳固然最好不過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底人類的身體構造是可以浮在水面上的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說人類身體70%由水構成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這個數值提升到80%會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將無限接近於水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了嗎  1班的竹田會游泳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在游泳池…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋怎麼啦  喝那麼多水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來要達到80%是無望了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的游泳課  我可是幹勁兒十足 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識1班的竹田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他昨天在游泳池學會游泳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個竹田終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我已經沒退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  沒退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧吧  現在與水無限接近的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺水喝太多了使得肚子有些凸起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那表情…前所未有的幹勁兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會給你打氣的  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  鼓起幹勁兒去游泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前先去下保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都別問給我纏上繃帶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來今天真熱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的班級真好  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一節課是游泳課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳技術長進了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你別問你還問
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能上游泳課真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我纏繃帶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  把大家視線都吸引到這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不會察覺稍稍有些凸起的肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  今天南的肚子凸出來了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓄水率剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  蓄水率是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛喝水想讓自己浮在水面上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田  吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我就是水的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根手指是怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是小小的擦傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了還是別游泳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  沒必要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天千秋你就在邊兒上看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能哭  好不容易積蓄的水分…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得那麼有幹勁兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天才剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是越熱越舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校的泳池真不盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想多游會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  明天去學校外的泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正休息嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳池？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那圭子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去最深的地方快樂地游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不怎麼想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  早早做準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢？不邀請其他人了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:14:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  以為她肯定會邀請藤岡我才去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  利子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來必須誘導她去邀請藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛南同學貌似說要去泳池…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  這雙怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙釘鞋真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這雙不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴死了  老爸老媽會買給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果露出一副想去泳池的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會邀請我去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去泳池這想法雖然不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但才三個人是不是有點兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得少了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好想去泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠上課那點兒完全不盡興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才剛游過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這天氣還真是熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去啊  學校以外的泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天剛好有空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出是故意而為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我知道他倆的心思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能責備完全未察覺到他倆話中含義的夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當不容易做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快察覺到吧  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個敏感的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說由我去邀請藤岡就萬事大吉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好難為情  還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…三個人太少的話再叫些人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是人多點兒比較開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好找個志同道合的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊  男女同行會更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人多  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志同道合的  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女同行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  我一個人在那邊瞎起勁兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了  我去邀請妹妹的朋友們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很滿意學校的泳池  不想去其它地方了吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪裡搞錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙已經起床了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假能早起真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:19:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懶床大王竟然早起可見太陽還是會從西邊昇起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惟獨每次出遊都會早起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不追過來？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈好像心情不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對她做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我們幾個人去了泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到我當鬼的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她生氣地指著我說「你到底想不想玩啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不想玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題…在游泳池怎麼能去隨便碰對方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了藤岡大家都是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當鬼的時候害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後滿臉通紅變作一隻赤鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你做個示範
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示範？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}touch{\r}\N碰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  很簡單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到玩捉迷藏的是夏奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別顧慮玩兒就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:21:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊  很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過三年冬馬也會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰女生是多麼的難
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹也是女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說過很危險了  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.95,0:22:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰  碰… 奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這麼容易讓你抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  你很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢間的捉迷藏越認真越有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決一勝負  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.71,0:23:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男子漢間的捉迷藏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出來  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.31,0:23:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢就堂堂正正的出來決一勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.39,0:23:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒…饒了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嘛  今年夏天要好好游個夠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股幹勁兒只是一時興起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回  南家三姐妹～歡迎回來～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想被沖走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次鼓起幹勁兒吧
